data.description: Enjoy the solitude in this rarely available Aruba 2 story Townhouse tucked away in a quiet corner in Island Walk. Perfect for entertaining your friends and family in this 3 bedroom, 2.5 bath, Open Floor Plan offering both a Living Room and Great Room open to the Kitchen & Dining Area...all overlooking your private pool. Relax in your generous Master Suite offering a spacious Walk-in closet, separate Tub & Shower & Dual Sinks. Working from home? Transform a Guest Bedroom into a private Home Office. Island Walk has Low Fees that includes Landscape & Lawn Care, Irrigation, HDTV & High-Speed Internet! Island Walk is an active community that is bustling with Activities and Amenities include a Towncenter, a resort style swimming pool. a lap pool, a fitness center, tennis courts, pickleball, bocce, a fantastic restaurant, post office, a gas station and car wash. DON'T MISS OUT! Make this YOUR ideal home in Paradise!
